text: First off let me say best casting in a comedy ever. i can totally see will ferrel and john lithgow as father and son and the same goes for mark whalberg and mel gibson. this movie is hilarious it had me laughing from start to finish. i was really happy with this film. i loved everything about it, the humor, the cast, the story, the directing and the music and the stunts were good too. this has to be one of will ferrel's best movies since elf, blades of glory and daddy's home. i'm not sure but there might be a third one. who knows. the chemistry between the cast was awesome they felt like a real family and hearing john cena sing made my day. loved this film. if you loved the first one you will love this one. this movie is cinematastic. if you have not seen this movie then i recommend you do rating 5/5
